('93416','32160','5','Modern golf villa on the golf course of Santa Ponsa '),
('93417','32161','5','Only a few minutes walk from the golf course and the "Santa Ponsa Country Club" away, sits this magnificent villa on a plot of 4.200m². \r\nThis villa was extensively renovated with high quality materials in 2013/14 and is now looking for a new owner. Over an impressive entrance you reach the main house with approx 550m² of living space. On the ground floor there is the entrance hall with office, living room, dining room with open plan modern fitted kitchen, pantry, family room with TV, music room, guest bathroom and a master bedroom with dressing room and bathroom en suite. On the 1st floor there are 3 more guest bedrooms each with a bathroom en suite. A separate guest house with living room, kitchenette and bedroom with bathroom en suite is for your guests available. In the midst of a Mediterranean-style garden there are a generous swimming pool with surrounding terraces, a playground and a covered barbecue and bar. From the property you have direct access to the golf course, even with a golf car. The sale price was rduced from 5.750.000€ to 4.950.000€ and  includes indoor - and outdoor furnitures aswell  a family golf share for the golf course St. Ponsa I. \r\n.\r\n'),
